::Feline::

She nodded,"Yeah, I'm fine."  She relaxed just a bit as he put his 
gun away.  But she didn't take her eyes off him. She stopped shaking, 
but still kept her back against the wall.  She moved her hips 
slightly and twitched her tail.  She relaxed her hands and retracted 
her claws.  But she didn't move and inch closer to him.

"I..I have to get these back to the CR chamber room and finish 
getting things ready."
